00:12:34.590 --> 00:12:36.790
- I feel like it's all
detours all the time.

00:12:37.830 --> 00:12:39.550
- For sure, it's a meander.

00:12:39.550 --> 00:12:43.973
My career has been a meander
more than a straight path,

00:12:45.150 --> 00:12:47.250
and discovery, and learning,

00:12:47.250 --> 00:12:49.550
and learning something new about myself,

00:12:49.550 --> 00:12:51.993
learning something new
about what I enjoy doing.

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:54.320
You know, we at Khan Academy

00:12:54.320 --> 00:12:56.390
really believe in a learning mindset,

00:12:56.390 --> 00:12:58.100
and I think that's what
May-Li was talking about.

00:12:58.100 --> 00:13:00.190
That's true in whatever
we're trying to learn,

00:13:00.190 --> 00:13:02.700
whether it's a subject we're
studying on Khan Academy,

00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:05.990
whether it's learning how
to be a better leader,

00:13:05.990 --> 00:13:07.510
some aspect of leadership.

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:09.830
And one thing that I think is interesting,

00:13:09.830 --> 00:13:13.420
May-Li just wanted to, to
