00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:28.950
or we'd like to think they have.

00:23:28.950 --> 00:23:32.390
And I think there are pockets of places

00:23:32.390 --> 00:23:35.800
where it's wonderful,
like we're here together,

00:23:35.800 --> 00:23:38.350
and we think, we hope we're helping

00:23:38.350 --> 00:23:41.030
to create an environment
that's a good one,

00:23:41.030 --> 00:23:44.020
