of discourse all the time.

00:23:44.020 --> 00:23:46.380
I don't know if things have moved, I mean,

00:23:46.380 --> 00:23:48.400
there's definitely more conversation,

00:23:48.400 --> 00:23:52.413
but I think the powers
that be dig in as well.

00:23:53.560 --> 00:23:55.400
So we have a lot more to do.

00:23:55.400 --> 00:23:56.673
- [Rachel] Right, that's true.

00:23:57.700 --> 00:24:00.310
Perhaps maybe when you
