00:24:00.310 --> 00:24:02.720
how would you think that it
would have changed perhaps?

00:24:02.720 --> 00:24:04.840
You know, what were
you thinking, like, oh,

00:24:04.840 --> 00:24:06.720
in 10 years, this won't be a problem

00:24:06.720 --> 00:24:07.553
because blah, blah, blah.

00:24:07.553 --> 00:24:09.020
What kind of was that that you kind of

00:24:09.020 --> 00:24:10.830
are maybe a little bit surprised still

00:24:10.830 --> 00:24:13.180
that you have to kind of
hit your head against?

00:24:16.390 --> 00:24:17.223
- Do you wanna take--

00:24:17.223 --> 00:24:19.950
- Yeah, I feel like I would have,

00:24:19.950 --> 00:24:21.586
