00:24:26.930 --> 00:24:28.700
I feel like I would have expected

00:24:28.700 --> 00:24:31.150
those needles to have
moved further by now.

00:24:31.150 --> 00:24:33.450
But, I mean, I think
we've seen the statistics

00:24:33.450 --> 00:24:36.450
of women in computer
science was like at 35%

00:24:36.450 --> 00:24:37.283
or something in the '80s,

