but I don't feel like that here.

00:37:00.060 --> 00:37:01.700
- [Rachel] Right, yeah.

00:37:01.700 --> 00:37:02.550
- Yeah, for sure.

00:37:03.620 --> 00:37:04.798
- [Rachel] Yeah, we don't do that here,

