there are things, I think,

00:37:16.440 --> 00:37:18.510
with women in the room there tends to be

00:37:18.510 --> 00:37:20.910
more of the asking others
for their thoughts.

00:37:20.910 --> 00:37:23.930
I think just, I do feel naturally

00:37:23.930 --> 00:37:27.845
there's often a little more
inclusion just in the room.

00:37:27.845 --> 00:37:29.860
- [Rachel] Right.

