00:47:57.240 --> 00:47:58.840
the biggest contributing factor.

00:47:58.840 --> 00:48:02.130
I think finding an environment,

00:48:02.130 --> 00:48:04.523
like the one that we feel we have here,

00:48:05.950 --> 00:48:07.790
super important, right?

00:48:07.790 --> 00:48:10.253
Because find a place you can thrive in.

00:48:11.520 --> 00:48:13.390
